{
  "texts": [
    "The research indicates that Chat GPT can contribute to this enhancement by promptly and accurately addressing student queries, generating concise summaries of course materials, and delivering personalized feedback on their assignments.",
    "The participants rated Chat GPT as easy to use, helpful, and accurate, with a high level of overall satisfaction [31].",
    "\"We Need to Talk About Chat GPT: The Future of AI and Higher Education\" by Neumann et al.",
    "is a timely and thoughtprovoking article that discusses the role of AI, specifically the Chat GPT language model, in higher education.",
    "The authors stress the necessity for a careful balance between the two and highlight significant concerns about the possible advantages and disadvantages of utilizing AI in education."
  ]
}